Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.73,0:22:27.36,ED English,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5}{\fad(250,250)}Trying to catch the white fragments of his dream,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.44,0:22:33.16,ED English,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5}{\fad(250,250)}a boy runs.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.16,0:22:36.99,ED English,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5}{\fad(250,250)}When he lets go,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.99,0:22:47.88,ED English,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5}{\fad(250,250)}it disappears into the sound of the wind in the distance.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.88,0:22:55.97,ED English,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5}{\fad(250,250)}The kindness that he once saw is now gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.97,0:23:06.90,ED English,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5}{\fad(250,0)}He steps forward alone, looking only at his feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.94,0:23:22.29,ED English,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5}{\fad(250,0)\3c&HCB6D14&\bord2\blur2}He always listened to the song that disappeared by morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.29,0:23:37.51,ED English,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5}{\fad(0,500)}He chased forever those footprints we left.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.48,0:00:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What I'm looking for might be the other you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.03,0:00:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,On the other side of this sky, there is a girl with wings.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.07,0:00:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,She spreads those wings and continues to be blown by the wind from the distant past, just like long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.80,0:00:36.59,Default,,0,0,0,,My mother passed away before she told me any more details.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.59,0:00:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Since then, my companions on the road have been just the story of the girl in the sky and this doll.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.85,0:00:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yukito-san, are you searching for the same girl that your mother sought?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.36,0:00:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, there's no way that you'd be that girl, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.40,0:00:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Many people have visions of flying in the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.20,0:00:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That girl can fly too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.66,0:00:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.70,0:01:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,She has wings.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.66,0:01:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.83,0:01:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I want wings too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.65,0:02:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.86,0:03:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, freeloader, here's a gift!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.32,0:03:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, a sloth.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.41,0:03:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't this better and more lovable than a dirty doll?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.25,0:03:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, I have to make you hurry and make money so you can leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.42,0:03:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It's cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.42,0:03:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,A glass after work really is the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.89,0:03:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like I live for these times!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.18,0:03:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, freeloader, first up tonight is the slightly-cryable-at-emotionally-moving-confession-of-love corner!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.19,0:03:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Do it yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.81,0:03:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Misuzu, are you sleepy?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.19,0:03:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm... I think so...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.36,0:03:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Come here. I'll let you use my lap as a pillow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.66,0:03:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?! I-It's okay; it's not like I'm still a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.28,0:03:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go to sleep now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.70,0:03:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.25,0:03:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Good night!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.80,0:04:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, she ran away.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.59,0:04:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you often let her use your lap as a pillow?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.01,0:04:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Stupid! It was a joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.01,0:04:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,As if that kid would cuddle with someone as pathetic as me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.85,0:04:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,That girl... Did she say "gao" today too?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.56,0:04:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.35,0:04:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I hit her each time she said it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.15,0:04:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,For some reason, when she was younger, she thought that a chick was a dinosaur's child.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.61,0:04:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, when she saw a chick at a summer festival booth, she really wanted it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.12,0:04:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,But at that time, we were poor, so we couldn't buy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.62,0:04:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Ever since then, she's had the habit of saying "gao" whenever something happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.55,0:04:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not cut out to be a parent.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.09,0:04:45.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I should have remained alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.51,0:04:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What's more, that girl is weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.51,0:04:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Weird?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.52,0:04:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,However, it seems that she is fine when she is with you,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.85,0:04:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,so if possible, stay friends with her forever,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.27,0:05:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,since it's already impossible for me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.44,0:05:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Come! It's the start of a fun puppet show!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.75,0:05:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.71,0:05:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's kind of creepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.96,0:06:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a feeling that it'll be in my dreams, in a bad way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.25,0:06:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.13,0:06:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.88,0:06:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me my payment!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.76,0:06:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't work at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.43,0:06:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Piko.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.10,0:06:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you again?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.85,0:06:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you say that your name was Potato?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.89,0:06:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Pikkori.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.39,0:06:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Piko.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.81,0:06:19.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Piko pikoo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.69,0:06:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Piko piko pika.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.15,0:06:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you trying to imitate?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.15,0:06:27.36,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,Is your daughter well?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.36,0:06:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.45,0:06:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,She says that white rice is yummy and eats many second-helpings, so it makes making meals worthwhile.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.95,0:06:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Please tell your daughter not to upset her stomach.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.16,0:06:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.58,0:06:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.63,0:06:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Now then...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.55,0:06:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing loitering in front of my place all this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.01,0:06:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, let's go home, shall we...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.89,0:06:54.35,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,Hey! Don't try so hard to ignore me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.97,0:06:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Potato, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.14,0:06:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You know him?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.44,0:07:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? Yukito-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.31,0:07:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yukito-kun is talking to Onee-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.48,0:07:06.02,Note,,0,0,0,,Sign: Kirishima Clinic
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.49,0:07:11.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, you're good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.70,0:07:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems that Potato has become your fan too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.45,0:07:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, did you say Kunisaki Yukito-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.54,0:07:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You have impressive skill, but I think that making money from that trick is impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.87,0:07:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Piko?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.88,0:07:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Piko!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.04,0:07:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Despite what it seems, I've been wandering from town to town, living off just this trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.34,0:07:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.05,0:07:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you've made loooooooooots of money in this town too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.05,0:07:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you haven't?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.14,0:07:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what do you think of working part-time at this clinic?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.48,0:07:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Kirishima Hijiri.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.98,0:07:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the only doctor here ever since my parents passed away.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.61,0:07:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I was looking for someone to do odd jobs.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.37,0:07:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Why bamboo?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.37,0:08:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.41,0:08:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I've wanted to do this at least once.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.75,0:08:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is today's lunch nagashi soumen?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.46,0:08:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,In this house, if Kano says nagashi soumen, we eat nagashi soumen.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.67,0:08:13.43,Default,,0,0,0,,This is obviously an unfair seating arrangement.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.43,0:08:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Why's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.64,0:08:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd eat a lot if you didn't sit there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.76,0:08:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Piko.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.64,0:08:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Piko...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.72,0:08:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'll see you tomorrow at the same time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.27,0:08:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll pay me more, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.85,0:08:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, as special treatment, I'll let you perform puppet shows in front of our place.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.28,0:08:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, I'll let you eat lunch too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.11,0:08:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It was fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.78,0:08:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's play again tomorrow, Yukito-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.62,0:08:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Pikopiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.74,0:08:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,See you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.74,0:08:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Piko pikopikoooo!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.58,0:08:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I make a mistake by accepting the job?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.38,0:08:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez, this town really doesn't have many people passing by.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.38,0:08:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess traffic accidents must be uncommon too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.76,0:08:58.97,Note,,0,0,0,,Sign: Niinuma Rice and Liquor Shop
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.30,0:08:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.26,0:08:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, no, it's my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.85,0:09:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.06,0:09:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Don't mind it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.64,0:09:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my responsibility too for bumping into you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.89,0:09:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,But why do you have such a large load?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.98,0:09:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,My daughter enjoys rice and eats well, so I just...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.11,0:09:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.90,0:09:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, this isn't much, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.49,0:09:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,N-N-No, it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.78,0:09:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't accept...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.87,0:09:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.78,0:09:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not much, but please accept this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.87,0:09:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Does this town not operate on any currency?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.75,0:09:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides that, what kind of daughter can eat that much rice?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.84,0:09:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Misuzu is late.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.65,0:09:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, a sloth!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.78,0:09:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,So cuuuuute...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.28,0:09:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, almost like a smaller version of Misuzu...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.08,0:10:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what happened to your parents?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.25,0:10:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.42,0:10:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you lost by any chance?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.59,0:10:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Want to eat it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.93,0:10:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It's yummy and cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.01,0:10:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Decide whether it's yummy or cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.68,0:10:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It's cute and yummy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.81,0:10:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.98,0:10:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Yukito-san, who's this girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.07,0:10:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently, she's lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.90,0:10:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.03,0:10:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Six years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.86,0:10:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What an incredible name.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.36,0:10:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yukito-san, you be quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.70,0:10:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.03,0:10:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You say that before your age, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.37,0:10:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Shino Saika, six years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.91,0:10:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Shino-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.33,0:10:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Byebye.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.83,0:10:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Mmhmm, byebye.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.75,0:10:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,That girl has to be hospitalized now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.59,0:11:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,She's sick?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.68,0:11:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.55,0:11:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it seems that it's not that bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.68,0:11:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,And she says that she's fine because sloth became her friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.64,0:11:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.19,0:11:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.40,0:11:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, of course you see dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.82,0:11:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I do too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.28,0:11:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,A mysterious dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.62,0:11:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,A dream of the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.25,0:11:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I was in the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.25,0:11:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,There was a world that I had never seen before.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.71,0:11:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,See, if I'm like this, the clouds are above me,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.26,0:11:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,but in my dream, the clouds were packed beneath my feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.97,0:11:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,From the gaps between the clouds, I could see the bright blue of the ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.02,0:11:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,But I couldn't even tell how far it was
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.89,0:11:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,because everything extended endlessly.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.02,0:11:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Say,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.99,0:12:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,did you have wings in your dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.36,0:12:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.32,0:12:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know; I didn't notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.45,0:12:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It's better if you don't talk to strangers about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.16,0:12:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.37,0:12:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I've only told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.34,0:12:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, it somehow fits so naturally.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.18,0:12:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have different ones?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.89,0:12:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The rest are too small.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.39,0:12:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm. smells nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.86,0:12:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.32,0:12:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,A boxed lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.40,0:12:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I made this one with utmost care, so it's extremely delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.95,0:12:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Boxed lunch?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.57,0:12:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You went to the trouble of...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.45,0:12:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Please deliver it to Kano.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.29,0:12:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.12,0:12:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.12,0:12:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Kano is at school again today to take care of the animals.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.87,0:12:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,If you eat it on the way there...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.59,0:13:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll deliver it carefully and quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.63,0:13:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Can we stop by the book store?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.30,0:13:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,There are quite a number of students.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.18,0:13:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,So the ones here have supplemental classes, club activities or student government, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.72,0:13:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Piko.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.52,0:13:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,This might be a good opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.60,0:13:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, please welcome my puppet show with much applause!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.82,0:13:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Woohoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.53,0:13:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Kunisaki, you're the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.20,0:13:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.20,0:13:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Kunisaki, you're the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.16,0:13:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Love and peace!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.12,0:13:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Kunisaki, you're the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.33,0:13:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way that could happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.29,0:13:33.04,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,Piko?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.66,0:13:34.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.45,0:13:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Piko.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.71,0:13:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,If I take such a weird creature in, the high school might erupt in a great panic.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.42,0:13:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't move from there until I tell you to.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.88,0:13:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Pikkori.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.26,0:13:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,There's something I'd like to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.59,0:13:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.43,0:13:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I've come to deliver a boxed lunch to someone named Kirishima Kano.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.51,0:13:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know where she is?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.93,0:13:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanorin?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.93,0:13:57.52,Note,,0,0,0,,[note: "-rin" is an ending put on names to make them sound cuter]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.93,0:13:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Kanorin... maybe she's still in the nurse's office?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.27,0:13:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Nurse's office?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.23,0:14:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.69,0:14:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,She said she was going to the rooftop because she wanted to feel the wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.78,0:14:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,She fell saying "kyuu~" after mumbling something.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.61,0:14:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it's just a little light-headedness.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.66,0:14:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.71,0:14:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,So you worried about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.33,0:14:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You're okay now, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.09,0:14:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez, you're overreacting.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.63,0:14:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I just felt a little dizzy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.22,0:14:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.30,0:14:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't the sky so high?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.18,0:14:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yukito-kun, can't you fly in the sky?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.39,0:14:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way I can fly.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.77,0:14:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,But you can move a doll.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.48,0:14:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Those things are completely unrelated.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.23,0:14:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, you said something like "If you could use magic," right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.03,0:14:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! That?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.32,0:14:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, because I can use magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.95,0:14:51.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.87,0:14:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a bit of a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.99,0:14:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't use it until I become an adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.04,0:14:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,But I've already decided what I'll do with my first spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.16,0:15:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.21,0:15:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.21,0:15:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you what I'll do second, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.09,0:15:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't particularly want to hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.42,0:15:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Aww?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.92,0:15:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.05,0:15:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't listen, it'll come out of your stomach, tear through crunchcrunching,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.93,0:15:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,and humankind will be unable to match their strength, so it'll be like "Oh, what a problem!"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.09,0:15:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,"The Earth, the Earth is in great trouble," eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.14,0:15:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.60,0:15:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to protect the Earth, the Earth!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.43,0:15:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, what do you want to do second?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.35,0:15:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.52,0:15:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to fly in the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.48,0:15:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Magic to fly in the sky...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.69,0:15:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.86,0:15:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Kunisaki Yukito!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.58,0:15:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't attack me so suddenly!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.37,0:15:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you angry,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.95,0:15:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,when I actually bothered to talk to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.46,0:15:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.83,0:15:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,My head is spinning.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.59,0:15:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What a dirty doll!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.88,0:15:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.84,0:15:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so worn.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.92,0:15:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Poor thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.09,0:15:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You're suffering under a stupid master, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.47,0:15:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't say that so poignantly!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.55,0:15:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, I'll save you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.51,0:15:58.06,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.93,0:15:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,See you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.72,0:16:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.44,0:16:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.65,0:16:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you a butt-shaking-ling?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.69,0:16:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, how far are you going?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.99,0:16:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.32,0:16:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.91,0:16:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,already!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.75,0:16:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Minagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.51,0:16:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.51,0:16:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, Minagi is the one fixing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.43,0:16:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, say "thank you".
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.05,0:16:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you telling me that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.01,0:16:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Ta-da.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.76,0:16:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It's done.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.77,0:16:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, it came out nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.39,0:16:43.39,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,Whoa... You're good.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.39,0:16:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh-hen!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.39,0:16:44.73,Note,,0,0,0,,[note: Japanese sound for showing pride.]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.31,0:16:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It must be a very important doll to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.11,0:16:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,since you're always carrying it around.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.69,0:16:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.19,0:16:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The shape of an important memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.86,0:16:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.66,0:16:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.99,0:17:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,No,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.74,0:17:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,that might be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.33,0:17:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You ruined the mood!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.42,0:17:06.83,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.96,0:17:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Presenting: rice ticket
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.96,0:17:11.42,Note,,0,0,0,,[on the ticket: Worldwide Rice Ticket 1000 Yen]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.76,0:17:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.51,0:17:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You're hungry, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.56,0:17:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't Tohno-san great?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.98,0:17:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Not only is she great at studying, but she can sew as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.82,0:17:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.57,0:17:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are we headed?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.94,0:17:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Where many people congregate.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.99,0:17:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,If you do a puppet show there, you'll have many customers.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.08,0:17:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.41,0:17:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Mummy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.70,0:17:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly what kind of job does she have?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.66,0:17:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.04,0:17:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe she went and prayed at the shrine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.59,0:17:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Shrine?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.25,0:17:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup, that's where we're headed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.38,0:17:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no one here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.72,0:17:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It's almost time for the summer festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.59,0:18:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, this shrine will be full of people
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.89,0:18:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,because children from the town will come.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.72,0:18:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,The kids from this town are all unruly.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.52,0:18:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Waah, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.06,0:18:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.15,0:18:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.40,0:18:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Since we've come this far, I thought we should play some more.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.86,0:18:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's play hide-and-seek.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.49,0:18:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.62,0:18:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Hide-and-seek.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.87,0:18:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to play it with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.45,0:18:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,How old do you think we are?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.58,0:18:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Then... Then... Bug catching.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.25,0:18:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Gao.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.47,0:18:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, a fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.34,0:18:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to catch fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.30,0:18:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't care what we play, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.81,0:18:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Since it's summer vacation, I want to play as much as I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.27,0:18:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Misuzu!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.78,0:18:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going now, got it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.36,0:19:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.09,0:19:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, do you still believe
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.55,0:19:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,that when a chick grows up, it'll become a dinosaur?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.60,0:19:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez, I know already.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.93,0:19:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,When a chick grows up, it'll become a chicken.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.90,0:19:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, what I wanted wasn't a chick or a dinosaur's child.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.40,0:19:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard that you cried all day.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.78,0:19:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It didn't matter what it was as long as Mummy bought it for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.21,0:19:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What a fun day!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.79,0:19:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.63,0:19:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.84,0:20:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't had a birthday this fun, so I'm really glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.88,0:20:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Today is... your birthday?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.09,0:20:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.93,0:20:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you keep quiet about something that important?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.01,0:20:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.76,0:20:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Because...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.39,0:20:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,If I knew, I would have tried to get you a present, at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.02,0:20:12.48,Note,,0,0,0,,[Paper: rice ticket]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.27,0:20:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yukito-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.52,0:20:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Go on home.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.57,0:20:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,No one would watch a puppet show at night, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.91,0:20:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's over already?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.66,0:20:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.62,0:20:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Show me, even if it's just a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.88,0:20:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, great.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.21,0:20:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.51,0:20:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,But a child probably wouldn't turn to watch this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.01,0:20:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It's none of your business!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.64,0:20:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.10,0:20:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.27,0:20:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I visited some acquaintances, but they weren't home.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.31,0:20:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll give it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.48,0:20:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,A thank you gift for showing me something unusual.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.70,0:21:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It's really good.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.24,0:21:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you lucky that I was given a cake?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.74,0:21:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup, and the number of candles matches my age.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.79,0:21:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if he was planning to celebrate someone's birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.71,0:21:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Does Haruko not remember that today is your birthday?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.96,0:21:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Mummy's busy, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.01,0:21:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Pretty...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.81,0:21:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,How is it, are you satisfied?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.31,0:21:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I'm happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.31,0:21:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Then let's go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.07,0:21:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Kano...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.78,0:21:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.74,0:21:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Kano!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.95,0:21:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The shrine again?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.78,0:21:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I think that she came here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.12,0:21:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.75,0:21:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,For example...
